<abstract><t>This document describes Segment Routing mapped to IPv6 (SRm6).  SRm6 is a Segment Routing (SR) solution that leverages IPv6.  It supports a wide variety of use-cases while remaining in strict compliance with IPv6 specifications.  SRm6 is optimized for ASIC-based forwarding devices that operate at high data rates.</t></abstract>

